ai-patthana17.30:0.2_0: (This should be expanded as in the teachings.)
ai-patthana17.30:1.1_0: Neither believe that gives rise to an undecided, and because of grasping.
ai-patthana17.30:2.1_0: There is no cause or reason for doing this.
ai-patthana17.30:2.1_2: When there are nine being born, growing old ...
ai-patthana17.30:3.1_0: I don’t give rise to diversity of views, revulsion, and grasped.
